channel.title: [317] Teleporting Help Please[317]
channel.description:
Hey Moparscape Community. Ok so I need some help so I came here to get it. So what I need is how do I teleport to the second level. Normaly when you teleport your on the grund floor, but I want to teleport to the 2nd Level. I want to make a few ladders functional to put shops above but I don't know how to. So please post below your suggestions.
Thanks.

item.title: [317] Teleporting Help Please[317]
item.dc:creator: @bily123 bily123
item.description:
@bily123 wrote:

[quote=“Dastan_, post:3, topic:358364”]go to your characters files , find your name in it.
enter it.
and on the top you should see this

character-height = 0 character-posx = 3686 character-posy = 3479
just edid the

character-height = 0

change 0 to whatever you want
0 = ground , 1 = second floor , 2 = third floor[/quote]
I think he/she is trying to say to go up a level then type ::mypos and get the coordinates that way.
